{\ottdrulename{lam}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleapp}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

\ottpremise{\Psi  \vdash  \ottnt{A}  \triangleright  \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \rightarrow  \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{2}}}}}%
\ottpremise{ \Psi   \vdash   \ottnt{e_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  :  \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{3}}}}  \otthl{ \rightsquigarrow   s_{{\mathrm{2}}} } }%
\ottpremise{\Psi  \vdash  \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{3}}}}  \lesssim  \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{1}}}}}%
}{
 \Psi   \vdash   \ottnt{e_{{\mathrm{1}}}} \, \ottnt{e_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  :  \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \otthl{ \rightsquigarrow   \ottsym{(}  \langle  \ottnt{A}  \hookrightarrow  \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \rightarrow  \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \rangle  s_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \ottsym{)} \, \ottsym{(}  \langle  \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{3}}}}  \hookrightarrow  \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \rangle  s_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \ottsym{)} } }{%
{\ottdrulename{app}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdrulelet}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

\ottpremise{ \Psi  \ottsym{,}  \ottmv{x}  \ottsym{:}  \ottnt{A}   \vdash   \ottnt{e_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  :  \ottnt{B}  \otthl{ \rightsquigarrow   s_{{\mathrm{2}}} } }%
}{
 \Psi   \vdash   \ottkw{let} \, \ottmv{x}  \ottsym{=}  \ottnt{e_{{\mathrm{1}}}} \, \ottkw{in} \, \ottnt{e_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  :  \ottnt{B}  \otthl{ \rightsquigarrow   \ottsym{(}  \lambda  \ottmv{x}  \ottsym{:}  \ottnt{A}  .\,  s_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \ottsym{)} \, s_{{\mathrm{1}}} } }{%
{\ottdrulename{let}}{}%
}}

\newcommand{\ottdruleasXXtvar}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \ottmv{a}  \ottsym{]}  \vdash  \ottmv{a}  \lesssim  \ottmv{a}  \dashv  \Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \ottmv{a}  \ottsym{]}}{%
{\ottdrulename{as\_tvar}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleasXXevar}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}  \vdash  \widehat{a}  \lesssim  \widehat{a}  \dashv  \Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}}{%
{\ottdrulename{as\_evar}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleasXXint}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash  \mathsf{Int}  \lesssim  \mathsf{Int}  \dashv  \Gamma}{%
{\ottdrulename{as\_int}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleasXXarrow}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \vdash  B_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \lesssim  A_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \dashv  \Theta}%
\ottpremise{\Theta  \vdash  \ottsym{[}  \Theta  \ottsym{]}  A_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \lesssim  \ottsym{[}  \Theta  \ottsym{]}  B_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \dashv  \Delta}%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash  A_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \rightarrow  A_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \lesssim  B_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \rightarrow  B_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \dashv  \Delta}{%
{\ottdrulename{as\_arrow}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleasXXforallR}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \ottsym{,}  \ottmv{a}  \vdash  A  \lesssim  B  \dashv  \Delta  \ottsym{,}  \ottmv{a}  \ottsym{,}  \Theta}%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash  A  \lesssim  \forall  \ottmv{a}  .\,  B  \dashv  \Delta}{%
{\ottdrulename{as\_forallR}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleasXXforallL}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \ottsym{,}   \blacktriangleright_{ \widehat{a} }   \ottsym{,}  \widehat{a}  \vdash  A  \ottsym{[}  \ottmv{a}  \mapsto  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}  \lesssim  B  \dashv  \Delta  \ottsym{,}   \blacktriangleright_{ \widehat{a} }   \ottsym{,}  \Theta}%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash  \forall  \ottmv{a}  .\,  A  \lesssim  B  \dashv  \Delta}{%
{\ottdrulename{as\_forallL}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleasXXforallLL}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \ottsym{,}   \blacktriangleright_{ \widehat{a}_S }   \ottsym{,}   \widehat{a}_{S}   \vdash  A  \ottsym{[}  \ottmv{a}  \mapsto   \widehat{a}_{S}   \ottsym{]}  \lesssim  B  \dashv  \Delta  \ottsym{,}   \blacktriangleright_{ \widehat{a}_S }   \ottsym{,}  \Theta}%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash  \forall  \ottmv{a}  .\,  A  \lesssim  B  \dashv  \Delta}{%
{\ottdrulename{as\_forallLL}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleasXXspar}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash  \mathcal{S}  \lesssim  \mathcal{S}  \dashv  \Gamma}{%
{\ottdrulename{as\_spar}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleasXXgpar}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash  \mathcal{G}  \lesssim  \mathcal{G}  \dashv  \Gamma}{%
{\ottdrulename{as\_gpar}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleasXXunknownL}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash  \star  \lesssim  A  \dashv  \Gamma}{%
{\ottdrulename{as\_unknownL}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleasXXunknownR}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash  A  \lesssim  \star  \dashv  \Gamma}{%
{\ottdrulename{as\_unknownR}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleasXXunknownLL}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash  \star  \lesssim  \mathbb{C}  \dashv  \ottsym{[}  \mathbb{C}  \ottsym{]}  \Gamma}{%
{\ottdrulename{as\_unknownLL}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleasXXunknownRR}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash  \mathbb{C}  \lesssim  \star  \dashv  \ottsym{[}  \mathbb{C}  \ottsym{]}  \Gamma}{%
{\ottdrulename{as\_unknownRR}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleasXXinstL}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{ \widehat{a}  \notin \textsc{fv} (  A  ) }%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}  \vdash  \widehat{a}  \lessapprox  A  \dashv  \Delta}%
}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}  \vdash  \widehat{a}  \lesssim  A  \dashv  \Delta}{%
{\ottdrulename{as\_instL}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleasXXinstR}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{ \widehat{a}  \notin \textsc{fv} (  A  ) }%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}  \vdash  A  \lessapprox  \widehat{a}  \dashv  \Delta}%
}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}  \vdash  A  \lesssim  \widehat{a}  \dashv  \Delta}{%
{\ottdrulename{as\_instR}}{}%
}}

\newcommand{\ottdefnaconsub}[1]{\begin{ottdefnblock}[#1]{$\Gamma  \vdash  A  \lesssim  B  \dashv  \Delta$}{}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleasXXtvar{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleasXXevar{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleasXXint{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleasXXarrow{}}

\ottusedrule{\ottdruleasXXforallLL{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleasXXspar{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleasXXgpar{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleasXXunknownL{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleasXXunknownR{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleasXXunknownLL{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleasXXunknownRR{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleasXXinstL{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleasXXinstR{}}
\end{ottdefnblock}}

\newcommand{\ottdruleinstlXXsolve}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \vdash  \tau}%
}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{,}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{,}  \Gamma'  \vdash  \widehat{a}  \lessapprox  \tau  \dashv  \Gamma  \ottsym{,}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{=}  \tau  \ottsym{,}  \Gamma'}{%
{\ottdrulename{instl\_solve}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinstlXXsolveU}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}  \vdash  \widehat{a}  \lessapprox  \star  \dashv  \Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}}{%
{\ottdrulename{instl\_solveU}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinstlXXsolveS}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \vdash  \tau}%
}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{,}   \widehat{a}_{S}   \ottsym{,}  \Gamma'  \vdash   \widehat{a}_{S}   \lessapprox  \tau  \dashv  \Gamma  \ottsym{,}   \widehat{a}_{S}   \ottsym{=}  \tau  \ottsym{,}  \Gamma'}{%
{\ottdrulename{instl\_solveS}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinstlXXsolveG}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \vdash  t}%
}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{,}   \widehat{a}_{G}   \ottsym{,}  \Gamma'  \vdash   \widehat{a}_{G}   \lessapprox  \tau  \dashv  \Gamma  \ottsym{,}   \widehat{a}_{G}   \ottsym{=}  t  \ottsym{,}  \Gamma'}{%
{\ottdrulename{instl\_solveG}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinstlXXsolveUS}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{[}   \widehat{a}_{S}   \ottsym{]}  \vdash   \widehat{a}_{S}   \lessapprox  \star  \dashv  \Gamma  \ottsym{[}   \widehat{a}_{G}   \ottsym{,}   \widehat{a}_{S}   \ottsym{=}   \widehat{a}_{G}   \ottsym{]}}{%
{\ottdrulename{instl\_solveUS}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinstlXXsolveUG}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{[}   \widehat{a}_{G}   \ottsym{]}  \vdash   \widehat{a}_{G}   \lessapprox  \star  \dashv  \Gamma  \ottsym{[}   \widehat{a}_{G}   \ottsym{]}}{%
{\ottdrulename{instl\_solveUG}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinstlXXreach}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{b}  \ottsym{]}  \vdash  \widehat{a}  \lessapprox  \widehat{b}  \dashv  \Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{b}  \ottsym{=}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}}{%
{\ottdrulename{instl\_reach}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinstlXXreachSGOne}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{[}   \widehat{a}_{S}   \ottsym{]}  \ottsym{[}   \widehat{b}_{G}   \ottsym{]}  \vdash   \widehat{a}_{S}   \lessapprox   \widehat{b}_{G}   \dashv  \Gamma  \ottsym{[}   \widehat{a}_{G}   \ottsym{,}   \widehat{a}_{S}   \ottsym{=}   \widehat{a}_{G}   \ottsym{]}  \ottsym{[}   \widehat{b}_{G}   \ottsym{=}   \widehat{a}_{G}   \ottsym{]}}{%
{\ottdrulename{instl\_reachSG1}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinstlXXreachSGTwo}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{[}   \widehat{b}_{S}   \ottsym{]}  \ottsym{[}   \widehat{a}_{G}   \ottsym{]}  \vdash   \widehat{a}_{G}   \lessapprox   \widehat{b}_{S}   \dashv  \Gamma  \ottsym{[}   \widehat{b}_{G}   \ottsym{,}   \widehat{b}_{S}   \ottsym{=}   \widehat{b}_{G}   \ottsym{]}  \ottsym{[}   \widehat{a}_{G}   \ottsym{=}   \widehat{b}_{G}   \ottsym{]}}{%
{\ottdrulename{instl\_reachSG2}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinstlXXreachOther}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{b}  \ottsym{]}  \vdash  \widehat{a}  \lessapprox  \widehat{b}  \dashv  \Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{b}  \ottsym{=}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}}{%
{\ottdrulename{instl\_reachOther}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinstlXXarr}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{a}_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \ottsym{,}  \widehat{a}_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \ottsym{,}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{=}  \widehat{a}_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \rightarrow  \widehat{a}_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \ottsym{]}  \vdash  A_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \lessapprox  \widehat{a}_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \dashv  \Theta}%
\ottpremise{\Theta  \vdash  \widehat{a}_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \lessapprox  \ottsym{[}  \Theta  \ottsym{]}  A_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \dashv  \Delta}%
}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}  \vdash  \widehat{a}  \lessapprox  A_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \rightarrow  A_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \dashv  \Delta}{%
{\ottdrulename{instl\_arr}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinstlXXforallR}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}  \ottsym{,}  \ottmv{b}  \vdash  \widehat{a}  \lessapprox  B  \dashv  \Delta  \ottsym{,}  \ottmv{b}  \ottsym{,}  \Theta}%
}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}  \vdash  \widehat{a}  \lessapprox  \forall  \ottmv{b}  .\,  B  \dashv  \Delta}{%
{\ottdrulename{instl\_forallR}}{}%
}}

\newcommand{\ottdefninstl}[1]{\begin{ottdefnblock}[#1]{$\Gamma  \vdash  \widehat{a}  \lessapprox  A  \dashv  \Delta$}{}

\newcommand{\ottdruleinstrXXsolve}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{,}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{,}  \Gamma'  \vdash  \tau  \lessapprox  \widehat{a}  \dashv  \Gamma  \ottsym{,}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{=}  \tau  \ottsym{,}  \Gamma'}{%
{\ottdrulename{instr\_solve}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinstrXXsolveU}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}  \vdash  \star  \lessapprox  \widehat{a}  \dashv  \Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}}{%
{\ottdrulename{instr\_solveU}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinstrXXsolveS}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \vdash  \tau}%
}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{,}   \widehat{a}_{S}   \ottsym{,}  \Gamma'  \vdash  \tau  \lessapprox   \widehat{a}_{S}   \dashv  \Gamma  \ottsym{,}   \widehat{a}_{S}   \ottsym{=}  \tau  \ottsym{,}  \Gamma'}{%
{\ottdrulename{instr\_solveS}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinstrXXsolveG}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \vdash  t}%
}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{,}   \widehat{a}_{G}   \ottsym{,}  \Gamma'  \vdash  \tau  \lessapprox   \widehat{a}_{G}   \dashv  \Gamma  \ottsym{,}   \widehat{a}_{G}   \ottsym{=}  t  \ottsym{,}  \Gamma'}{%
{\ottdrulename{instr\_solveG}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinstrXXsolveUS}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{[}   \widehat{a}_{S}   \ottsym{]}  \vdash  \star  \lessapprox   \widehat{a}_{S}   \dashv  \Gamma  \ottsym{[}   \widehat{a}_{G}   \ottsym{,}   \widehat{a}_{S}   \ottsym{=}   \widehat{a}_{G}   \ottsym{]}}{%
{\ottdrulename{instr\_solveUS}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinstrXXsolveUG}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{[}   \widehat{a}_{G}   \ottsym{]}  \vdash  \star  \lessapprox   \widehat{a}_{G}   \dashv  \Gamma  \ottsym{[}   \widehat{a}_{G}   \ottsym{]}}{%
{\ottdrulename{instr\_solveUG}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinstrXXreach}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{b}  \ottsym{]}  \vdash  \widehat{b}  \lessapprox  \widehat{a}  \dashv  \Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{b}  \ottsym{=}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}}{%
{\ottdrulename{instr\_reach}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinstrXXreachSGOne}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{

\newcommand{\ottdruleinstrXXreachSGTwo}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinstrXXreachOther}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{

\newcommand{\ottdruleinstrXXarr}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

\ottpremise{\Theta  \vdash  \ottsym{[}  \Theta  \ottsym{]}  A_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \lessapprox  \widehat{a}_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \dashv  \Delta}%

\newcommand{\ottdruleinstrXXforallL}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

{\ottdrulename{instr\_forallL}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinstrXXforallLL}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

}{
\Gamma  \ottsym{[}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{]}  \vdash  \forall  \ottmv{b}  .\,  B  \lessapprox  \widehat{a}  \dashv  \Delta}{%
{\ottdrulename{instr\_forallLL}}{}%

\newcommand{\ottdruleinfXXlamann}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

}}

}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinfXXapp}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \vdash  e_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \Rightarrow  A  \dashv  \Theta_{{\mathrm{1}}}}%
\ottpremise{\Theta_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \vdash  \ottsym{[}  \Theta_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \ottsym{]}  A  \triangleright  A_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \rightarrow  A_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \dashv  \Theta_{{\mathrm{2}}}}%
\ottpremise{\Theta_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \vdash  e_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \Leftarrow  \ottsym{[}  \Theta_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \ottsym{]}  A_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \dashv  \Delta}%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash  e_{{\mathrm{1}}} \, e_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \Rightarrow  A_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \dashv  \Delta}{%
{\ottdrulename{inf\_app}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinfXXanno}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \vdash  A}%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \vdash  e  \Leftarrow  A  \dashv  \Delta}%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash  e  \ottsym{:}  A  \Rightarrow  A  \dashv  \Delta}{%
{\ottdrulename{inf\_anno}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleinfXXlet}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \vdash  e_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \Rightarrow  A  \dashv  \Theta}%
\ottpremise{\Theta  \ottsym{,}  \widehat{a}  \ottsym{,}  \ottmv{x}  \ottsym{:}  A  \vdash  e_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \Leftarrow  \widehat{a}  \dashv  \Delta  \ottsym{,}  \ottmv{x}  \ottsym{:}  A  \ottsym{,}  \Theta'}%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash  \ottkw{let} \, \ottmv{x}  \ottsym{=}  e_{{\mathrm{1}}} \, \ottkw{in} \, e_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \Rightarrow  \widehat{a}  \dashv  \Delta}{%
{\ottdrulename{inf\_let}}{}%
}}

\newcommand{\ottdefninf}[1]{\begin{ottdefnblock}[#1]{$\Gamma  \vdash  e  \Rightarrow  A  \dashv  \Delta$}{}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleinfXXvar{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleinfXXint{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleinfXXlamann{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleinfXXlam{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleinfXXlamPP{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleinfXXapp{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleinfXXanno{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleinfXXlet{}}
\end{ottdefnblock}}

%% defn chk
\newcommand{\ottdrulechkXXgen}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \ottsym{,}  \ottmv{a}  \vdash  e  \Leftarrow  A  \dashv  \Delta  \ottsym{,}  \ottmv{a}  \ottsym{,}  \Theta}%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash  e  \Leftarrow  \forall  \ottmv{a}  .\,  A  \dashv  \Delta}{%
{\ottdrulename{chk\_gen}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdrulechkXXlam}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \ottsym{,}  \ottmv{x}  \ottsym{:}  A  \vdash  e  \Leftarrow  B  \dashv  \Delta  \ottsym{,}  \ottmv{x}  \ottsym{:}  A  \ottsym{,}  \Theta}%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash  \lambda  \ottmv{x}  .\,  e  \Leftarrow  A  \rightarrow  B  \dashv  \Delta}{%
{\ottdrulename{chk\_lam}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdrulechkXXsub}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \vdash  e  \Rightarrow  A  \dashv  \Theta}%
\ottpremise{\Theta  \vdash  \ottsym{[}  \Theta  \ottsym{]}  A  \lesssim  \ottsym{[}  \Theta  \ottsym{]}  B  \dashv  \Delta}%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash  e  \Leftarrow  B  \dashv  \Delta}{%
{\ottdrulename{chk\_sub}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdrulechkXXlet}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \vdash  e_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \Rightarrow  A  \dashv  \Theta}%
\ottpremise{\Theta  \ottsym{,}  \ottmv{x}  \ottsym{:}  A  \vdash  e_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \Leftarrow  B  \dashv  \Delta  \ottsym{,}  \ottmv{x}  \ottsym{:}  A  \ottsym{,}  \Theta'}%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash  \ottkw{let} \, \ottmv{x}  \ottsym{=}  e_{{\mathrm{1}}} \, \ottkw{in} \, e_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \Leftarrow  B  \dashv  \Delta}{%
{\ottdrulename{chk\_let}}{}%
}}

\newcommand{\ottdefnchk}[1]{\begin{ottdefnblock}[#1]{$\Gamma  \vdash  e  \Leftarrow  A  \dashv  \Delta$}{}
\ottusedrule{\ottdrulechkXXgen{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdrulechkXXlam{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdrulechkXXsub{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdrulechkXXlet{}}
\end{ottdefnblock}}
